 699          //--------------------------------------------------
 700          // Description  : Read data to the External EEPROM by IIC
 701          // Input Value  : usSubAddr    --> Start address of selected device
 702          //                usLength     --> Numbers of data we want to read
 703          //                pReadArray   --> Result array
